HEADWORD: Lateness
<hw>Late"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state,
condition, or quality, of being late; <as>as, the <ex>lateness</ex> of
his arrival; the <ex>lateness</ex> of the hour; the <ex>lateness</ex> of
the season.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

